name: Make Happy Be True Genesis X Act Uganda

metadata.description: Make Happy Be True Genesis X Actuganda is an NFT project that partners with Act Uganda to change lives. Your help can empower 2280 NFT girls to become superheroes, warriors, magicians, and more. The first 500 mints are free, with 500 uncommon NFTs that will receive airdrops and whitelist status for our next charity partnership. 50% of the project's profits will be donated to Act Uganda, our charity partner. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make a difference and be a part of something special. Buy now and join our community.
metadata.name: Make Happy Be True Genesis#1
